<h2 id="support-comparison">📞 Support Quality Comparison</h2>

Support quality varies dramatically by tier on both platforms. At Glofox's Growth tier and above, our team consistently experiences sub-4-hour response times and competent first-contact resolution. Their support team understands fitness operations.

Mindbody's standard support has declined since their 2023 restructuring. Expect 12-24 hour initial response times at lower tiers. Enterprise customers report significantly better experiences with dedicated account managers, but that access requires Ultimate tier or above.

Both platforms offer extensive knowledge bases. Mindbody's documentation is more comprehensive; Glofox's is more current and easier to navigate.

